<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是万圣节呀！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对我来说是特别的日子，
只要一年中有这么一天，<delay20 />
我就能感到幸福了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家好像都很热衷于<delay20 />
打扮成恐怖的样子<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真吓人啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这事先姑且不论，<delay20 />应该不会有真的鬼怪<delay20 />
在万圣节出没吧？</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不给糖，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就捣蛋<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不给糖，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就捣蛋<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了等下讨糖果的时候<delay20 />能够声音悦耳，<delay20 />
我正在练习呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />万圣节活动前的倒计时<delay20 />
已经开始了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还没准备好的话可要抓紧啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />今天的<tag a="110" b="10" /><delay20 />
也许会显得和往日不同，格外兴高采烈。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这也是因为万圣节的魔法吗？</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />终于要开始了，万圣节活动！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也差不多<delay20 />
该准备起来了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯？<delay20 />你问准备什么？<10_4 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当然是为了提高乔装的完成度，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />做进入角色的意象训练呀！</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是刚才在散步路上看到的，<delay20 />
我们这座岛上也终于开始<delay20 />
摆出南瓜家具了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />看来不仅仅是我一个人<delay20 />
意识到万圣节接近的脚步呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />南瓜家具的陈列渐渐多了起来，<delay20 />
万圣节气氛也一点一点地<delay20 />
变得浓厚<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到节日到来之前，<delay20 />
这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上会有更多装饰被摆出来，<delay20 />
我就越来越期待了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="8" />的景色<delay20 />
也因为被万圣节气息浸染<delay20 />
而变得丰富多彩起来了呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />被这么多<delay20 />
万圣节风格的装饰包围，<delay20 />
有一种奇妙的感觉油然而生。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我就享受一下这样的风景吧，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />趁这万圣节的魔法还未解除<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
</msbt>